<plot>The film "Homesick", is a tale about a Central Florida architect named Timothy Zeit who has lost his heart to finish building a dream house for his family. When a category 4 hurricane comes to destroy everything that he has left, Tim tries to save his house. However, when all hope is lost, Tim finally asks the storm to destroy him inside his own unfinished house. Tim battles the hurricane overnight and through the darkness of the storm he finds the heart to rebuild again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?244316</url></doc>
